wiki.summary: “Foot Fungus” had been previewed many times, raising hype around the song in the few months prior to its release. While many expected the title to be “Okay,” Ski took to his Instagram to announce that the titles of his album’s tracks had been changed, and the song’s name was eventually “Foot Fungus”. The song is produced by Kenny Beats, which also worked with Ski on the song “Unbothered,” also on "STOKELEY". “Foot Fungus” debuted and peaked at #81 on the Billboard Hot 100 in the week of December 15, 2018. Read more on Last.fm.
